_sText:
This is my revised version the download files are completly new i just added a few more things in the map. Examples.
- Map name changed to de_temple_kbd because its dedicated to my clan |KBD|'s 2v2 tournament.
- Switched Bombsites around.
- A lot of cover at B. (Old A)
- Different Boxes at A.
- Less cover inside of tunnels.
- Added barrels inbetween CT Spawn and Tunnels.
- Moved the T Spawn back further to even the teams
-Eliminated the first section of gate near t Spawn to eliminate to fast of Rushing to B.
- Revised for a 2v2 tournament.
- Raised the trimming above temple so you can run on it rather than duck.
- Quicker CT Rushes because of raised displacements.
- More lighting in Tunnels and Temple.
- Eliminated Fog because of the advantage for CTs inside Temple and Tunnels.
- Better environmental lighting.
- A few other small details like easier ledge climbing.

Please redownload and reasses. Last time the old map was up it had full 10/10s but all the raitings got deleated. Please drop a comment if you download it.

Added 1 new Screenshot Thanks to FPS Banana.

(More Screenshots www.reliancecrew.com/temple.html)
